  "detailed_description": "<strong><i><u>\"Runestone: Pathfinder\"</u></i></strong> is a 3D adventure platformer game set in the world of Runestone. Players will play as a rookie pathfinder and help the rookie get through his first trial.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/84adcad158eefceb3c447dc80cb343fa.avif?t=1707900920\" width=636 height=96 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/58114fc4a2a4829eeaf3eb471082e65e.avif?t=1707900920\" width=446 height=96 /></span><br>    Movements, jumps, and dashes are consistent. You can combo them into more complex moves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/2845482db458e99f8dae87da03bf7caa.poster.avif?t=1707900920\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/2845482db458e99f8dae87da03bf7caa.webm?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/2845482db458e99f8dae87da03bf7caa.mp4?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/752b6e0cec23ab42370cb7d58a4c9411.avif?t=1707900920\" width=596 height=96 /></span><br>    You can expect a packed level with collectibles and achievements that take multiple playthroughs to accomplish. <br>    A fruitful adventure awaits you! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/0413d00b7b360000c307bf1c135112fe.poster.avif?t=1707900920\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/0413d00b7b360000c307bf1c135112fe.webm?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/0413d00b7b360000c307bf1c135112fe.mp4?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/fe2f76e0cee7f54b8ad8738e7081bda0.avif?t=1707900920\" width=596 height=96 /></span><br>    You might finish the first playthrough in one hour or two. You will improve the timer drastically the second time. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/60355fb25e8db50cf4c852c4cb250178.poster.avif?t=1707900920\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/60355fb25e8db50cf4c852c4cb250178.webm?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/60355fb25e8db50cf4c852c4cb250178.mp4?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/283f87b7a4427be8bdaa63b1725c728f.avif?t=1707900920\" width=596 height=96 /></span><br>    You can unlock and choose<br>-7(or more?) styles of feather color<br>-4 styles of backpacks<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/e26249ba19e7861e19dbc1d0cc733c51.avif?t=1707900920\" width=552 height=408 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/94193fbb3629c1ce4ae972e4cd37e399.avif?t=1707900920\" width=596 height=96 /></span><br>    Compete against players around the world to see who is the better Pathfinder!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/e788844f04f1ede061f364b143bb3dcb.avif?t=1707900920\" width=594 height=456 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong><i><u>\"Runestone: Pathfinder\"</u></i></strong> is a 3D adventure platformer game set in the world of Runestone. Players will play as a rookie pathfinder and help the rookie get through his first trial.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/84adcad158eefceb3c447dc80cb343fa.avif?t=1707900920\" width=636 height=96 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/58114fc4a2a4829eeaf3eb471082e65e.avif?t=1707900920\" width=446 height=96 /></span><br>    Movements, jumps, and dashes are consistent. You can combo them into more complex moves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/2845482db458e99f8dae87da03bf7caa.poster.avif?t=1707900920\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/2845482db458e99f8dae87da03bf7caa.webm?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/2845482db458e99f8dae87da03bf7caa.mp4?t=1707900920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/752b6e0cec23ab42370cb7d58a4c9411.avif?t=1707900920\" width=596 height=96 /></span><br>    You can expect a packed level with collectibles and achievements that take multiple playthroughs to accomplish. <br>    A fruitful adventure awaits you! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764080/extras/0413d00b7b360000c307b